{% extends "_base.html.j2" %}
{% block content %}
<p>Hi {{ pic | default('there') }},</p>

<p>Quick note — we have some excellent <strong>{{ rate_type | default('FAK') }}</strong> rates on <strong>{{ pol | default('HCM') }} → {{ pod }}</strong> that I thought might interest {{ company }}:</p>

{% if best_rate %}
<div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-left:4px solid #2196F3;padding:15px;margin:15px 0">
<strong>{{ best_rate.carrier }}</strong> — ${{ best_rate.amount }} / {{ best_rate.container }}<br>
<span style="color:#666">Valid until {{ best_rate.exp }}</span>
</div>
{% endif %}

<p>These rates are all-inclusive (O/F + surcharges). We handle {{ commodity | default('general cargo') }} shipments daily on this lane.</p>

<p>Happy to send a full breakdown if you're shipping soon. Just reply with your cargo details and I'll prepare a quote within the hour.</p>

<p>Cheers,</p>
{% endblock %}
